### Test JWT Authentication

### 1. Login để lấy JWT token
POST https://localhost:7000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "testpass"
}

### 2. Validate JWT token (thay YOUR_TOKEN_HERE bằng token từ response trên)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/auth/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "YOUR_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### 3. Test protected endpoint (sẽ tạo sau)
GET https://localhost:7000/api/chat/test
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE